Document: class_ResourceImporterImage
Path: godot/classes/class_resourceimporterimage.rst
Summary: This importer processes Image resources for 2D/3D use, differing from CompressedTexture2D handling.

This importer imports Image resources, as opposed to CompressedTexture2D. If you need to render the image in 2D or 3D, use ResourceImporterTexture instead.
